%202019%2C%20India%20accounts%20for%2026%20per%20cent%20of%20the%20global%20population%20using%20the%20dark%20web%2C%20the%20highest%20usage%20worldwide.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EEase%20of%20Doing%20Business%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20what%20we%20know%20of%20the%20highly%20opaque%20dark%20web%2C%20and%20how%20the%20drug%20market%20survives%20and%20thrives%20in%20India.%20There's%20no%20clarity%20on%20the%20number%20of%20people%20on%20the%20dark%20web%20in%20India%20because%20of%20its%20very%20nature%2C%20which%20provides%20complete%20concealment.%20As%20one%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ftopic%2Fcryptocurrency%5C%22%3Ecrypto%3C%2Fa%3E%20expert%2C%20who%20wishes%20to%20remain%20anonymous%2C%20explains%20with%20a%20laugh%3A%20'Even%20college%20students%20are%20now%20using%20it%20to%20get%20their%20assignments%20ghostwritten%20for%20a%20fee.%20What%20is%20clear%20is%20that%20the%20number%20has%20been%20increasing%20every%20year.%20In%20the%20early%20years%2C%20people%20did%20not%20know%20how%20to%20use%20or%20access%20it%2C%20but%20now%20the%20browser%20is%20publicly%20available%2C%20making%20downloading%20easier.%20And%20it's%20free.%20There's%20no%20clarity%20on%20the%20age%20group%20that%20is%20the%20most%20active%20on%20these%20dark%20websites%20either.%20What%20is%20clear%20and%20apparent%20is%20the%20stuff%20that's%20up%20for%20sale.%20Betting%2C%20drugs%2C%20child%20pornography%20and%20data%20leakage.%20The%20dark%20web%20is%20flooded%20with%20Aadhaar%20details%20and%20passwords%20of%20unsuspecting%20Indian%20citizens.%20People%20in%20India%20are%20very%20lax%20about%20their%20passwords.%20While%20the%20largest%20bucket%20of%20money%20in%20India%20currently%20is%20in%20the%20betting%20market%2C%20scamsters%20abound%20with%20private%20and%20leaked%20details%20of%20many%20ordinary%20Indians.'%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMore%20and%20more%20people%20are%20buying%20their%20drugs%20on%20the%20dark%20web%20than%20at%20any%20other%20time%20in%20recorded%20history.%20In%20the%202021%20Global%20Drug%20Survey%2C26%20researchers%20found%20that%20in%202020%2C%2015%25%20of%20survey%20participants%20who%20reported%20using%20drugs%20in%20the%20previous%20twelve%20months%20had%20obtained%20them%20from%20dark%20web%20marketplaces-either%20by%20purchasing%20them%20first-hand%20or%20via%20someone%20else.%20There%20was%20a%20three-fold%20jump%20in%20the%20percentage%20of%20such%20people%20since%202014%2C%20which%20is%20when%20the%20survey%20first%20started%20measuring%20the%20trend.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHow%20does%20the%20now%20flourishing%20drug%20market%20work%20for%20a%20buyer%20and%20seller%20on%20the%20dark%20web%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EStep%20one%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Select%20a%20website.%20Buyers%20usually%20pick%20one%20with%20a%20high%20reputation%20for%20delivering%20on%20time.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EStep%20two%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Create%20an%20account%20and%20username%20on%20that%20website.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EStep%20three%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20A%20wallet%20address%20will%20be%20given%20for%20the%20purchase%20plus%20a%20time%20limit.%20The%20buyer%20needs%20to%20pay%20within%20that%20time%20and%20share%20a%20screenshot%20confirming%20the%20payment%20is%20done.%20The%20moment%20the%20payment%20is%20okayed%2C%20the%20order%20will%20be%20processed.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5CnTwo%20features%20are%20key%20in%20this%20process%20-%20that%20there%20is%20a%20middleman%2C%20the%20handler%20of%20the%20website%2C%20and%20that%20the%20payment%20will%20only%20be%20made%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fbitcoin-marks-15-years-all-you-need-to-know-about-worlds-1st-cryptocurrency-4910959%5C%22%3Ecrypto%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fdrug-dealers-on-the-dark-web-used-cryptocurrency-to-launder-7-2-million-3793439%5C%22%3EBitcoin%20remains%20the%20most%20popular%3C%2Fa%3E%20coin%20for%20these%20sales%20and%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Flsd-drug-haul-by-ncb-biggest-drug-haul-in-2-decades-trade-through-dark-net-cryptocurrency-4098314%5C%22%3Edrugs%20available%3C%2Fa%3E%20range%20from%20purple%20hash%20to%20various%20types%20of%20cocaine%2C%20the%20highest%20quality%20of%20weed%2C%20LSD%2C%20and%20MDMA%2C%20more%20commonly%20known%20as%20Ecstasy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20players%20in%20India%20are%20among%20the%20smartest%2C%20frequently%20changing%20the%20names%20of%20their%20sites%2C%20ensuring%20that%20the%20actual%20coordinates%20of%20where%20these%20lethal%20substances%20are%20is%20never%20ever%20revealed.%20While%20very%20little%20is%20known%20about%20them%2C%20veterans%20in%20the%20field%20allude%20to%20a%20type.%20'Techies'%2C%20as%20they%20are%20often%20called%20-%20young%20people%20with%20brilliant%20minds%20for%20all%20things%20technology%2C%20and%20perhaps%20a%20taste%20for%20crime.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Arrest%20of%20Dipu%20Singh%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20twenty-one-year-old%20bachelor%20in%20hotel%20management%20from%20Amity%20University%20in%20Lucknow%2C%20Dipu%20Singh's%20social%20media%20pictures%20show%20a%20sharply%20dressed%20young%20man%20in%20a%20suit%2C%20with%20a%20well-groomed%20beard%20and%20a%20big%20smile.%20The%20son%20of%20a%20retired%20Army%20officer%2C%20Dipu%20looked%20like%20he%20had%20a%20bright%20and%20exciting%20future%20waiting%20for%20him.%20Until%20he%20was%20arrested%20by%20the%20NCB%20on%2031%20January%202020.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20NCB%20describes%20Dipu%20Singh%20as%20India's%20first%20narcotics%20vendor%20on%20the%20dark%20web%20to%20be%20caught.%20He%20is%20allegedly%20the%20mastermind%20behind%20hundreds%20of%20drug%20parcels%20clandestinely%20couriered%20to%20countries%20like%20the%20US%2C%20the%20UK%2C%20and%20many%20in%20Europe%2C%20using%20the%20dark%20web%20and%20crypto.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20started%20off%20under%20the%20commonest%20of%20garbs-sex%20pills.%20Dipu%20started%20with%20shipping%20medicines%20related%20to%20erectile%20dysfunction%20and%20fitness%20supplements%20to%20overseas%20locations%20using%20the%20dark%20web.%20When%20he%20saw%20the%20profit%20margins%20in%20psychotropic%20drugs%2C%20his%20game%20plan%20changed.%20He%20soon%20became%20a%20major%20player%20on%20the%20dark%20web%3B%20his%20listings%20were%20found%20in%20some%20of%20the%20biggest%20and%20reliable%20dark%20web%20markets%20like%20Empire%20Market%20and%20Majestic%20Garden.%20Orders%20were%20procured%20from%20the%20dark%20web%20and%20routed%20through%20secure%20messaging%20platforms%20like%20Wickr%20and%20WhatsApp.%20As%20his%20fame%20grew%2C%20so%20did%20his%20markets.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Operation%20Trance'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnbeknownst%20to%20him%2C%20the%20International%20Narcotics%20Control%20Board%20had%20started%20an%20investigation%20in%20December%202019%20to%20gather%20information%20from%20officers%20in%20different%20countries%20about%20these%20shipments.%20The%20NCB%20was%20now%20part%20of%20a%20global%20'Operation%20Trance'%20that%20saw%20joint%20intelligence%20gathering%20action%20on%20international%20postal%2C%20express%20mail%2C%20and%20courier%20shipments%20containing%20psychotropic%20drugs%20that%20are%20abused%20as%20sedatives%20and%20painkillers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20December%202019%20alone%2C%20NCB%20officials%20from%20Delhi%20and%20Mumbai%20seized%20over%2055%2C000%20psychotropic%20tablets%20worth%20Rs%2045%20lakh%2C%20from%20Delhi%2C%20Mumbai%2C%20and%20the%20UK.%20In%20early%20January%202020%2C%20customs%20officials%20in%20Delhi%20seized%20a%20package.%20Its%20source%20was%20traced%20to%20Lucknow%2C%20and%20all%20trails%20led%20to%20Dipu%20Singh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20name%20was%20listed%20as%20an%20active%20vendor%20on%20Empire%20Market.%20He%20was%20working%20under%20the%20username%20'Mr%20Robo'%20and%20had%20created%20fake%20IDs%20and%20tried%20to%20purchase%20a%20few%20drugs.%20Investigations%20showed%20payment%20gateways%20of%20cryptocurrencies%20like%20Bitcoins%20and%20Litecoin%20were%20used%20by%20the%20operators%20to%20conceal%20the%20transactions%20from%20regulatory%20agencies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ESmall%20Fish%20In%20A%20Giant%20Ocean%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESingh's%20interrogation%20-%20as%20pieced%20together%20from%20news%20reports%20and%20the%20Narcotics%20Bureau's%20own%20tweets%20-%20revealed%20that%20he%20was%20brought%20into%20the%20drug%20syndicate%20in%202018%20by%20a%20man%20who%20operates%20an%20online%20pharmacy%2C%20which%20had%20offered%20him%20a%20job%20to%20deliver%20medicines%20online.%20By%20early%202019%2C%20Singh%20associated%20with%20dark%20web%20markets%20and%20began%20supplying%20psychotropic%20tablets%20illegally%20to%20clients%20abroad.%20At%20last%20count%2C%20he%20had%20sent%20over%20600%20consignments%20of%20drugs%20using%20the%20dark%20web%20and%20used%20crypto%20as%20his%20channel%20for%20payments.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20investigating%20authorities%20assert%20this%20is%20a%20big%20win%2C%20critics%20are%20quick%20to%20point%20out%20these%20arrests%20are%20small%20fish%20in%20a%20giant%20ocean.%20As%20Macksofy%20founder%20Yasir%20Shaikh%20explains%2C%20drug%20cartels%20and%20the%20associated%20gang%20warfare%20that%20comes%20with%20the%20turf%20have%20now%20moved%20online.%20That%20means%20attacks%20are%20frequently%20launched%20against%20the%20websites%20of%20competitors%20to%20take%20them%20offline.%20By%20selling%20directly%20to%20users%2C%20dealers%20are%20slashing%20risk%2C%20cutting%20middlemen%2C%20and%20boosting%20profit%20margins.%20But%20players%20like%20Dipu%20Singh%20represent%20extremely%20small%20proportions%20of%20a%20market%20that%20is%20booming%20globally.%20So%2C%20while%20small%20vendors%20sometimes%20get%20caught%2C%20the%20big%20players%20keep%20changing%20their%20names%2C%20and%20their%20cat-and-m