%20in%20a%20cold%20room%20in%20Mainpuri%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20Shubha%20faced%20a%20dilemma%20regarding%20procuring%20seeds%20or%20saffron%20bulbs.%20She%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20content%20with%20simply%20ordering%20them%20from%20Kashmir%20without%20assessing%20the%20quality%20and%20gaining%20insights%20from%20local%20farmers.%20To%20address%20this%2C%20the%20family%20embarked%20on%20a%20trip%20to%20Kashmir%20for%20a%20week%2C%20engaging%20with%20farmers%2C%20immersing%20themselves%20in%20the%20cultivation%20process%2C%20and%20learning%20the%20dos%20and%20don%E2%80%99ts%20directly%20from%20the%20locals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20met%20about%2025%20to%2030%20farmers%20in%20Kashmir%20and%20spent%20many%20days%20with%20them.%20We%20wanted%20to%20learn%20about%20the%20kind%20of%20soil%20they%20use%2C%20the%20process%20of%20cultivating%20saffron%2C%20how%20long%20it%20takes%2C%20and%20which%20temperatures%20saffron%20thrives%20in.%20We%20also%20bought%20the%20bulbs%20from%20them%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Ankit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20coming%20back%2C%20Shubha%20set%20up%20a%20cold%20storage%20room%20of%20560%20square%20feet%20and%20started%20with%202%2C000%20kg%20of%20saffron%20bulbs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EHow%20do%20you%20grow%20saffron%20indoors%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20getting%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F345755%2Fhow-to-grow-saffron-at-home-indoors-ramesh-gera-noida-akarshak-institute-online-course%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esaffron%20bulbs%20from%20Kashmir%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20look%20like%20garlic%20pods%2C%20the%20first%20step%20was%20to%20dry%20them%20in%20a%20room%20and%20later%20aerate%20them%20for%20three%20days.%20They%20had%20to%20be%20checked%2C%20cleaned%20and%20turned%20every%20few%20hours%20by%20hand%2C%20which%20is%20traditionally%20done%20by%20women%20in%20Kashmir.%