g%20them%201%2C200%20km%20away%20was%20a%20massive%20task.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20Kashmir%2C%20the%20bud%20receives%20light%20only%20when%20it%20comes%20out%20of%20the%20soil.%20Learning%20at%20what%20stage%20that%20happens%20and%20providing%20the%20right%20temperature%20was%20the%20biggest%20challenge.%20When%20we%20started%2C%20we%20placed%20bulbs%20in%2018%20racks%20in%20six%20rows%20and%20provided%20different%20temperatures%20and%20light%20to%20each%20rack%20to%20judge%20which%20one%20worked%20the%20best%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20Ankit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20achieve%20this%2C%20Shubha%20and%20Ankit%20went%20through%2010%20years%20of%20saffron%20production%20data%20in%20Kashmir.%20They%20found%20that%20the%20best%20harvest%20was%20achieved%20in%202015-16%20and%20replicated%20the%20temperatures%20of%20that%20year.%20They%20developed%20a%20programme%20using%20IoT%20devices%20and%20sensors%20to%20maintain%20the%20right%20conditions%20and%20a%20controlled%20environment%20through%20aeroponics.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20about%2060%20days%2C%20the%20beautiful%20purple%20flower%20emerged%20and%20was%20ready%20for%20harvest!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fsaffron-1713440138.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20saffron%20from%20Shubhavni%20farms%20is%20sold%20online%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fsaffron-1713440138.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fsaffron-1713440138-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fsaffron-1713440138-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fsaffron-1713440138-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com