umbai.%20During%20his%20conversation%2C%20Chunky%20Panday%20revealed%20that%20there%20was%20a%20time%20when%20Shah%20Rukh%20Khan%20was%20living%20with%20his%20wife%2C%20interior%20designer%20Gauri%20Khan%2C%20in%20a%20rented%20house.%20The%20actor%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20think%20one%20of%20his%20first%20friends%20in%20Bombay%20when%20he%20arrived%20was%20my%20younger%20brother%20Chikki%20%5BPanday%5D.%20They're%20still%20the%20best%20of%20friends.%20So%2C%20at%20that%20time%2C%20they%20(Shah%20Rukh%20Khan%20and%20Gauri%20Khan)%20were%20renting%20a%20place%20and%20they%20used%20to%20come%20to%20meet%20my%20brother%2C%C2%A0%3Ci%3Esab%20baith%20ke%20video%20cassettes%20dekhte%20the%3C%2Fi%3E.%20So%20he%20and%20Gauri%20were%20in%20my%20house%20quite%20often.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChunky%20Panday%20added%20that%20he%20always%20believed%20that%20Shah%20Rukh%20Khan%20would%20%E2%80%9Cbecome%20a%20superstar%E2%80%9D.%20He%20added%2C%20%E2%80%9CWith%20Shah%20Rukh%2C%20I%20was%20so%20sure%20this%20boy%20is%20gonna%20become%20a%20superstar.%20Because%20he%20had%20that%20in%20him%2C%20you%20can%20see%20that%20fire%E2%80%A6He's%20always%20had%20that.%20That%20talent%20has%20always%20been%20there%20with%20him%20before%20he%20became%20the%20superstar.%20So%20he's%20very%20confident%20and%20he%20knew%20where%20he%20was%20going.%20I%20mean%2C%20yeah%2C%20of%20course%20very%20proud%20that%20I've%20known%20him%20since%20then.%20He%20hasn't%20changed.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBefore%20this%2C%20Chunky%20Panday's%20daughter%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fentertainment%2Fwhen-shah-rukh-khan-called-suhana-her-friend-ananya-his-lucky-charm-after-kkrs-first-ipl-win-5327382%5C%22%3Eactress%20Ananya%20Panday%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20revealed%20that%20she%20spent%20a%20lot%20of%20time%20at%20Shah%20Rukh%20Khan's%20house%20during%20her%20childhood.%20In%20an%20interview%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FC5C6HU8NCVS%2F%3Futm_source%3Di