nd%20received%20a%20few%20keyframes.%20Further%2C%20scanning%20those%20keyframes%20through%20Google%20Lens%2C%20the%20Desk%20found%20a%20Twitter%20post%20shared%20on%20April%2015%2C%20which%20carried%20the%20same%20video.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHere%20is%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fravishumar146%2Fstatus%2F1779593749229891596%5C%22%3Ethe%20link%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fweb.archive.org%2Fsave%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fravishumar146%2Fstatus%2F1779593749229891596%5C%22%3Earchive%20link%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20below%20is%20a%20screenshot%20of%20the%20same%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20further%20scanning%20the%20Google%20Lens%20search%20results%2C%20the%20Desk%20found%20that%20a%20similar%20video%20was%20uploaded%20on%20YouTube%20from%20the%20official%20channel%20of%20'Satyamev%20Jayate'%2C%20a%20chat%20show%20hosted%20by%20Aamir%20Khan%2C%20which%20was%20telecasted%20on%20Star%20Plus%20channel.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHere%20is%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DbJyQ9NhZCtk%5C%22%3Ethe%20link%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20the%20video%20titled%2C%20%26quot%3BSatyamev%20Jayate%20S1%20%7C%20Episode%2013%20%7C%20The%20Idea%20of%20India%20%7C%20Liberty%20(Hindi)%26quot%3B%2C%20which%20was%20published%20on%20August%2030%2C%202016%2C%20and%20below%20is%20a%20screenshot%20of%20the%20same%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20description%20of%20the%20video%20read%3A%20%26quot%3BStay%20tuned%20to%20the%20new%20season%20of%20Satyamev%20Jayate%2C%20starting%20March%202%2C%20every%20Sunday%2C%2011%20AM%20onwards%20only%20on%20STAR%20Plus.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Desk%20noticed%20that%20Khan's%20outfit%20and%20the%20red%20glowing%20light%20at%20the%20bottom%20of%20the%20video%20was%20the%20same%20as%20in%20the%20viral%20video.%20Below%20is%20a%20combination%20image%2C%20comparing%20the%20visuals%20of%20the%20two%20videos%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Desk%20listened%20to%20this%2040-second%20video%20and%20noticed%20t