%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Explained%3A%20How%20EVMs%20Record%20Your%20Vote%2C%20And%20How%20VVPAT%20System%20Works%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EPolling%20for%20the%20first%20phase%20of%20Lok%20Sabha%20election%20is%20being%20held%20amid%20a%20legal%20battle%20in%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20over%20Electronic%20Voting%20Machines%20(EVM).%20The%20petitioners%20have%20sought%20100%25%20cross-verification%20of%20votes%20cast%20on%20EVMs%20with%20paper%20slips%20generated%20through%20the%20VVPAT%20system.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20arguments%2C%20suggestions%20to%20revert%20to%20the%20ballot%20voting%20system%20have%20also%20come%20up%2C%20with%20the%20petitioners%20pointing%20to%20the%20European%20nations.%20The%20court%2C%20however%2C%20has%20told%20the%20petitioners%20not%20to%20make%20such%20comparisons%2C%20observing%20that%20the%20population%20of%20West%20Bengal%20is%20more%20than%20that%20of%20Germany.%20Yesterday%2C%20the%20Election%20Commission%20of%20India's%20counsel%20explained%20how%20the%20EVM%20system%20works%20and%20why%20it%20is%20foolproof%20against%20any%20form%20of%20tampering.%20The%20petitioners%20have%20raised%20the%20issue%20of%20the%20trust%20of%20voters%20in%20the%20system%20and%20sought%20tweaks%20in%20the%20current%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHere%20is%20a%20rundown%20of%20what%20an%20EVM%20is%20and%20how%20it%20is%20used%20for%20voting%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2Fglpnrn7o_control-unit_625x300_19_April_24.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EEVM%3A%20The%20Machine%20And%20Components%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20EVM%20has%20two%20units%20--%20the%20control%20unit%20and%20the%20balloting%20unit.%20These%20are%20connected%20by%20a%20cable.%20The%20EVM's%20control%20unit%20is%20with%20the%20presiding%20officer%2C%20also%20known%20as%20polling%20officer.%20The%20balloting%20unit%20is%20kept%20in%20the%20voting%20compartment%2C%20where%20people%20cast%20their%20votes.%20The%20balloting%20unit%20is%20usually%20covered%20on%20all%20sides%20for%20the%20voter's%20privacy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20voting%20booth%2C%20the%20polling%20officer%20verifies%20your%20identity%20and%20then%20presses%20the%20ballot%20button%20that%20enables%20you%20to%20vote.%20On%20the%20ballot%20unit%20are%20candidates%20names%20and%20symbols%20with%20blue%20buttons%20next%20to%20them.%20The%20voter%20has%20to%20press%20the%20button%20next%20to%20the%20name%20of%20the%20candidate%20of%20his%2Fher%20choice.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Voting%20Process%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20control%20unit%20with%20the%20polling%20officer%20has%20multiple%20buttons.%20One%20of%20them%20is%20titled%20'ballot'.%20Once%20the%20officer%20presses%20this%20button%2C%20a%20red%20light%20titled%20'busy'%20comes%20alive.%20This%20indicates%20that%20the%20control%20unit%20is%20ready%20to%20record%20a%20single%20vote.%20A%20green%20light%20on%20the%20ballot%20unit%2C%20where%20the%20voter%20is%2C%20switches%20on%2C%20signalling%20that%20the%20machine%20is%20ready%20for%20voting.%20The%20voter%20then%20presses%20the%20button%20next%20to%20the%20name%20of%20the%20candidate%20of%20his%2Fher%20choice.%20The%20ballot%20unit%20also%20has%20Braille%20script%20for%20visually-impaired%20voters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOnce%20the%20voter%20casts%20the%20vote%2C%20the%20control%20unit%20emits%20a%20beep%20sound%2C%20indicating%20that%20the%20voting%20is%20complete.%20The%20control%20unit%20also%20has%20an%20LED%20screen%20and%20buttons%20that%20can%20be%20used%20to%20see%20the%20total%20number%20of%20votes%20recorded%20on%20it.%20After%20all%20votes%20are%20recorded%2C%20the%20polling%20officer%20presses%20a%20button%20on%20the%20side%20of%20the%20control%20unit%2C%20sealing%20the%20machine.%20On%20counting%20day%2C%20a%20button%20titled%20'result'%20is%20used%20to%20see%20candidates-wise%20total%20votes.%20There%20is%20also%20a%20'clear'%20button%20that%20can%20be%20used%20to%20erase%20all%20data%20from%20the%20control%20unit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2Ful2ccgeg_ballot-unit_625x300_19_April_24.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20Is%20The%20VVPAT%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20VVPAT%20--%20Voter%20Verified%20Paper%20Audit%20Trail%20--%20enables%20a%20voter%20to%20see%20if%20the%20vote%20was%20cast%20properly%20and%20went%20to%20the%20candidate%20he%2Fshe%20supports.%20Once%20a%20voter%20presses%20the%20button%20next%20to%20the%20name%20of%20the%20candidate%20of%20choice%2C%20the%20VVPAT%2C%20which%20is%20connected%20to%20the%20control%20unit%20and%20ballot%20unit%2C%20generates%20a%20paper%20slip%20that%20is%20visible%20to%20the%20voter%20for%20seven%20seconds.%20After%20that%2C%20the%20paper%20slip%20falls%20into%20a%20dropbox%20in%20the%20VVPAT%20machine.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECurrently%2C%20votes%20recorded%20on%205%20VVPAT%20machines%20are%20cross-checked%20with%20the%20EVMs%20in%20every%20Assembly%20segment.%20The%20petitions%20in%20Supreme%20Court%20want%20100%25%20cross-checking%20of%20VVPAT%20slips%20with%20votes%20recorded%20on%20EVMs.%20The%20petitioners%20have%20also%20sought%20that%20the%20seven-second%20light%20on%20the%20VVPAT%20stays%20on%20so%20that%20the%20voter%20can%20check%20if%20his%2Fher%20vote%20has%20been%20recorded%20properly.%20Another%20suggestion%20was%20to%20issue%20the%20paper%20slip%20to%20voters.%20The%20Election%20Commission%20has%20contested%20this%2C%20saying%20it%20affects%20voter%20secrecy%20and%20may%20be%20misused.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Case%20For%20EVM%20System%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20Election%20Commission%2C%20the%20EVM%20system%20is%20foolproof.%20The%20poll%20body%20says%20it%20saves%20vote%20counting%20time%2C%20is%20tamper-proof%20and%20user-friendly.%20It%20is%20also%20lightweight%20and%20robust%20--%20this%20is%20critical%20in%20a%20country%20where%20polling%20officials%20have%20to%20trek%20long%20distances%20and%20even%20climb%20hills%20to%20reach%20far-flung%20polling%20booths.%20The%20EVM%20is%20capable%20of%20self-diagnosis%20and%20is%20a%20standalone%20machine.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20EVMs%20do%20not%20need%20electricity%20and%20come%20with%20battery%2Fpower%20packs.%20This%20is%20again%20a%20crucial%20feature%20that%20enables%20voting%20in%20areas%20that%20do%20not%20have%20a%20stable%20power%20supply.%20Well%20before%20every%20election%2C%20a%20First%20Level%20Checking%20(FLC)%20of%20EVMs%20and%20VVPATs%20is%20carried%20out.%20During%20this%20check%2C%20the%20data%20on%20the%20EVMs%20is%20erased%20and%20the%20functionality%20of%20different%20components%20is%20screened.%20This%20check-up%20is%20carried%20out%20in%20the%20presence%20of%20representatives%20of%20political%20parties.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1713504480000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2Fg060sih8_election-evm_625x300_19_April_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fevm-vvpat-lok-sabha-election-2024-as-india-votes-today-a-look-at-how-evm-and-vvpat-polling-machines-work-5474620%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Polling%20for%20the%20first%20phase%20of%20Lok%20Sabha%20election%20is%20being%20held%20amid%20a%20legal%20battle%20in%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20over%20Electronic%20Voting%20Machines%20(EVM).%20The%20petitioners%20have%20sought%20100%25%20cross-verification%20of%20votes%20cast%20on%20EVMs%20with%20VVPAT%20paper%20slips%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia