0reports%20emerged%20of%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fisrael-iran-war-live-updates-israel-strikes-hit-iran-airport-tehran-says-shot-down-several-drones-10-facts-5474259%5C%22%3EIsraeli%20strike%20on%20an%20Iranian%20airport%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpaceX%20is%20a%20California-based%20spacecraft%20manufacturer%20and%20satellite%20communications%20firm%20owned%20by%20Musk.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20tech%20entrepreneur%20made%20a%20two-day%20trip%20to%20Israel%20last%20November%2C%20during%20which%20Prime%20Minister%20Benjamin%20Netanyahu%20took%20him%20on%20a%20tour%20of%20an%20Israeli%20kibbutz%20destroyed%20during%20Hamas's%20October%207%20attack.%20After%20his%20Israel%20visit%2C%20Hamas%20had%20invited%20him%20to%20Gaza%20to%20see%20the%20extent%20of%20destruction%20caused%20by%20Israeli%20bombardment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIsrael%20had%20retaliated%20with%20air%20attacks%20on%20Gaza%20after%20the%20October%207%20attack%2C%20sparking%20the%20war%20that%20has%20been%20raging%20for%20the%20past%20six%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStarlink%2C%20a%20satellite%20internet%20network%20owned%20by%20SpaceX%2C%20won%20a%20license%20this%20February%20to%20operate%20in%20Israel%20and%20parts%20of%20the%20Gaza%20Strip.%20The%20Israel%20government%20had%20said%20it%20approved%20the%20use%20of%20Starlink's%20services%20at%20a%20field%20hospital%20in%20Gaza.%20Starlink%20has%20also%20agreed%20to%20prevent%20Hamas%20from%20getting%20access%20to%20its%20internet%20services.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1713504180000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-02%2Ffrr9q5p_elon-musk-reuters_625x300_02_February_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fisrael-iran-conflict-send-rocket-to-stars-elon-musks-cryptic-post-amid-middle-east-tensions-5474625%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Elon%20Musk%2C%20the%20world's%20richest%20man%2C%20has%20made%20an%20apparent%20call%20for%20peace%20amid%20heightened%2