en%20it%20comes%20to%20his%20role%20in%20the%20Indian%20Premier%20League%20(IPL)%202024%20season.%20The%20seasoned%20seamer%20has%20emerged%20as%20the%20wrecker-in-chief%20for%20his%20franchise%2C%20picking%20up%20wickets%20at%20regular%20intervals%2C%20but%20he%20wants%20more%20responsibilities%20on%20his%20shoulders.%20After%20emerging%20as%20the%20player%20of%20the%20match%20for%20his%20franchise%20in%20the%20Indian%20Premier%20League%20(IPL)%202024%20match%20against%20Punjab%20Kings%20on%20Thursday%2C%20Bumrah%20made%20it%20clear%20to%20the%20skipper%20Hardik%20Pandya%20the%20role%20he%20wants%20to%20play.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBurmah's%20figures%20of%203%20for%2021%20in%204%20overs%20proved%20to%20be%20the%20difference%20as%20Mumbai%20Indians%20beat%20Punjab%20Kings%20by%209%20runs.%20After%20the%20game%2C%20however%2C%20Bumrah%20said%20that%20he%20wants%20to%20be%20bowling%20in%20the%20powerplay%20early%20on%20when%20the%20ball%20is%20offering%20some%20swing.%20This%20season%2C%20his%20role%2C%20however%2C%20has%20been%20quite%20different.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMuch%20closer%20game%20than%20what%20we%20thought.%20Want%20to%20make%20an%20impact%20early%20on.%20In%20this%20format%2C%20the%20ball%20swings%20for%20two%20overs%2C%20and%20you%20want%20to%20make%20use%20of%20that.%20This%20format%20is%20a%20little%20difficult%20for%20the%20bowlers%20because%20the%20batsmanship%20is%20going%20over%2C%20plus%20the%20time%20restrictions%20and%20the%20Impact%20Player%20rule.%20What%20you%20can%20do%20is%20prepare%20your%20best%20and%20back%20yourself.%20Go%20out%20there%20and%20give%20your%20best.%20I%20try%20to%20relay%20messages%20from%20wherever%20I%20am%20on%20the%20field.%20You%20don't%20want%20to%20give%20too%20many%20messages%2C%26quot%3B%20Bumrah%20said%20in%20the%20post-match%20presentation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20Mumbai%20Indians%2C%20the%20likes%20of%20Haridk%20Pandya%2C%20Gerald%20Coetzee%20and%20Akash%20Madhwal%20have%20been%20used%20more%20in%20the