could%20train%20with%20in%20Manipur%20who%20could%20take%20my%20game%20to%20the%20next%20level.%20So%2C%20I%20conveyed%20this%20message%20to%20Roshan%20and%20said%20I%20needed%20to%20train%20outside%20Manipur%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20recalls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201080px)%20100vw%2C%201080px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FChungreng-ground-and-pound-1713276782.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Chungreng%20Koren%20competing%20at%20an%20MFN%20event%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FChungreng-ground-and-pound-1713276782.jpg%201080w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FChungreng-ground-and-pound-1713276782-300x200.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FChungreng-ground-and-pound-1713276782-500x333.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FChungreng-ground-and-pound-1713276782-768x512.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FChungreng-ground-and-pound-1713276782-150x100.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-347398%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22720%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EChungreng%20Koren%20competing%20at%20an%20MFN%20event%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20this%20conversation%2C%20Chungreng%20got%20a%20call%20from%20a%20fellow%20fighter%20whom%20he%20had%20met%20earlier%20in%20Bengaluru%2C%20and%20heard%20that%20there%20was%20a%20gym%20there%20that%20wanted%20to%20recruit%20fighters.%20He%20was%20told%20that%20the%20gym%20there%20would%20take%20care%20of%20all%20his%20living%20expenses.%20So%2C%20he%20came%20back%20to%20Bengaluru%20once%20again%20and%20began%20training.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20second%20stint%20in%20Bengaluru%20would%20change%20Chungreng%E2%80%99s%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHere%2C%20I%20met%20Coach%20Ashwin%20Hoon%20of%20Warrior%E2%80%99s%20Cove%20MMA%2C%20a%20gym%20based%20out%20of%20Gurugram%2C%20who%20was%20there%20for%20a%20seminar.%20I%20loved%20the%20way%20he%20was%20teaching%20us%20and%20the%20techniques%20he%20was%20showing%20us%2C%20but%20more%20than%20that%2C%20he%20was%20just%20a%20very%20good%20person.%20I%20knew%20that%20if%20I%20trained%20under%20him%2C%20I%20would%20improve.%20He%20was%20the%20coach%20I%20was%20looking%20for%20all%20this%20time.%20I%20didn%E2%80%99t%20care%20about%20dropping%20the%20sponsorship%20I%20was%20getting%20in%20Bengaluru.%20So%2C%20I%20spoke%20to%20Ashwin%20Sir%20and%20made%20my%20way%20to%20Delhi-NCR%20to%20train%20at%20Warrior%E2%80%99s%20Cove%20MMA%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20recalls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-captioned%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FC4c5xolpyjQ%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FC4c5xolpyjQ%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3EView%20this%20post%20on%20Instagram%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FC4