0suicide%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20Harishchandra%20Sude%2C%20the%20founder%20of%20the%20non-profit%20Grameen%20Shramik%20Pratishthan%2C%20was%20asked%20about%20his%20childhood%20aspirations%2C%20his%20response%20was%20rather%20peculiar%20and%20profound.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20recalls%20how%20during%20an%20Independence%20Day%20celebration%2C%20where%20each%20student%20was%20required%20to%20share%20their%20dreams%20and%20aspirations%2C%20he%20had%20stood%20up%20and%20promptly%20declared%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20want%20to%20create%20a%20world%20where%20everyone%20helps%20each%20other%3B%20a%20world%20envisioned%20by%20Gandhi%20himself!%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20many%20may%20have%20smiled%20at%20young%20Harishchandra%E2%80%99s%20aspirations%2C%20little%20did%20they%20know%20that%20this%20determined%20boy%20would%20go%20on%20to%20empower%20over%201%2C000%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F326708%2Fdattu-agarwal-free-residential-school-for-girls-with-visual-impairment%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20people%20with%20visual%20impairment%20a%3C%2Fa%3End%20other%20disabilities%20%E2%80%94%20granting%20them%20autonomy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20past%2043%20years%2C%20through%20his%20organisation%2C%20he%20has%20been%20providing%20them%20with%20training%20in%20acupressure%2C%20loom%20operation%2C%20and%20graphic%20designing%20in%20digital%20media.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EThe%20journey%20to%20independence%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHarishchandra%20is%20the%20first%20university%20graduate%2C%20not%20only%20in%20his%20family%20but%20also%20in%20his%20entire%20village.%20Despite%20being%20a%20young%20man%20with%20extraordinary%20dreams%2C%20societal%20expectations%20nudged%20him%20towards%20seeking%20employment%20in%20the%20bustling%20%E2%80%9Cbig%20cities%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERecalling%20those%20pivotal%20moments%2C%20he%20shares%2C%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20you%E2%80%99re%20the%20first%20in%20your%20family%20or%20village%20to%20successfully%20graduate%20from%20university%2C%20all%20eyes%20are%20on%20you.%20My%20father%20and%20the%20villagers%20anticipated%20that%20I%20would%20secure%20a%20job%20and%20contribute%20financially%20to%20the%20household.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20Harishchandra%E2%80%99s%20aspirations%20diverged%20from%20conventional%20expectations.%20He%20explains%2C%20%E2%80%9CFrom%20a%20very%20young%20age%2C%20I%20realised%20that%20certain%20segments%20of%20society%20receive%20little%20to%20no%20assistance.%20They%20are%20often%20marginalised%20and%20forced%20to%20depend%20on%20others.%20Securing%20a%20job%20was%20never%20my%20intention%3B%20my%20goal%20was%20to%20assist%20the%20overlooked%20sections%20of%20society.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENow%20fondly%20called%20the%20%E2%80%98Angel%20for%20the%20disabled%E2%80%99%2C%20Harishchandra%E2%80%99s%20childhood%20was%20a%20far%20cry%20from%20being%20happy%20or%20secure.%20%E2%80%9CI%20was%20only%20a%20young%20child%20of%20five%20years%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F231564%2Fcovid-19-coronavirus-india-vaccine-history-smallpox-rabies-science-facts-trivia%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20when%20I%20caught%20smallpox.%3C%2Fa%3E%20Due%20to%20the%20disease%2C%20I%20lost%20vision%20in%20one%20of%20my%20eyes%20and%20developed%20lots%20of%20scars%20on%20my%20face%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20young%20boy%20survived%20the%20disease%2C%20he%20became%20an%20outsider%20to%20other%20kids%20in%20the%20village.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20scars%20on%20my%20face%20and%20the%20loss%20of%20vision%20made%20me%20a%20%E2%80%98difficult%20child%E2%80%99.%20My%20mother%2C%20who%20was%20always%20worried%20about%20me%2C%20passed%20away%20the%20same%20year%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%2