se%20children%20use%20their%20skills%20to%20become%20independent%2C%20he%20thought.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENoble%2C%20though%20his%20idea%20was%2C%20Karthikeyan%20lacked%20the%20resources%20and%20formal%20training%20to%20set%20up%20something%20of%20this%20scope.%20But%20a%20trip%20through%20India%20in%202012%20would%20be%20the%20ray%20of%20hope%20he%20needed.%20As%20he%20voyaged%20through%20South%20India%2C%20he%20stumbled%20upon%20%E2%80%98kanthari%E2%80%99%20which%20was%20built%20on%20the%20premise%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F333854%2Fdigital-resource-centres-nasscom-dxc-technology-empower-youth-women-skill-building-business-support%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eempowering%20people%3C%2Fa%3E%20who%20had%20a%20dream%20to%20drive%20social%20change%20in%20their%20communities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CDo%20you%20have%20a%20vision%20but%20lack%20the%20tools%20to%20start%20an%20NGO%3F%E2%80%9D%20Sabriye%20Tenberken%2C%20co-founder%20of%20kanthari%2C%20had%20asked%20Karthikeyan%20around%2013%20years%20ago%2C%20almost%20reading%20his%20mind.%20His%20answer%20was%20affirmative.%20And%20since%20that%20day%20there%20has%20been%20no%20looking%20back.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThrough%20the%20seven%20months%20he%20spent%20on%20kanthari%E2%80%99s%20Thiruvananthapuram%20campus%2C%20Karthikeyan%E2%80%99s%20earliest%20impressions%20were%20that%20of%20the%20endeavour%20being%20an%20answer%20to%20his%20prayers.%20%E2%80%9COften%20when%20I%20would%20tell%20people%20about%20my%20dream%2C%20they%20would%20scoff.%20But%20at%20kanthari%2C%20it%20was%20the%20opposite.%20Everyone%20would%20tell%20me%20my%20goals%20were%20achievable.%20Along%20with%20the%20right%20encouragement%2C%20I%20also%20got%20training%20in%20corporate%20communication%2C%20fundraising%2C%20designing%20a%20social%20venture%2C%20writing%20the%20concept%20note%2C%20pitching%20to%20investors%2C%20and%20speaking%20to%20the%20media%2C%E2%8